        "faq_item_BaHyjk": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Description",
            "content": "<p>The bag your routine deserves. Crafted in soft pebbled vegan leather with a structured silhouette that holds its shape whether it's sitting on your vanity or tucked inside a carry-on. The gold-tone zipper opens wide for easy access, and the interior fits your Vera Lane essentials — foundation, brush, and then some — without the bulk.</p><p>Embossed with the Vera Lane logo for a quietly luxurious finish. Because even the in-between moments of your routine should feel intentional.</p><ul><li>Pebbled vegan leather, soft to the touch</li><li>Gold-tone metal zipper with branded pull</li><li>Compact enough for travel, roomy enough for your daily kit</li><li>Easy-wipe interior lining</li></ul>",
            "faq_show_image": false,
            "faq_enable_popup": false,
            "faq_popup_trigger_text": "View full list",
            "faq_popup_title": "FULL LIST OF INGREDIENTS",
